### POST /api/v1/admin/ops/outbox/{id}/reprocess
### Descripción: Reprocesar dead-letter desde ops. Requiere rol Admin o Support. Solo mensajes en dead-letter.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 204 No Content | 404 | 400 { "error": "Only dead-letter messages can be reprocessed." }

# @name reprocessOutboxOps
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/ops/outbox/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/reprocess
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Response esperado (204):
### (sin body)

### Response error (404): Not Found
### Response error (400): { "error": "string" }
